‚óŹ The pkg_config crate with statik(true) can emit cargo:rustc-link-lib=
  directives itself. The issue is that when you call .probe() with statik(true),
   the crate emits its own cargo: directives including potentially empty lib
  names. The problem is the pkg_config crate itself is emitting the empty lib
  name, not our loop.

  Let me check by looking at the cargo output more carefully.

